Ms. H. T. Loan, born in 1976 (member # 010107050014). She lives with her husband and 2 school age children in the hamlet of Van Thuong. Her family works in farming; in addition she does selling at the market and her husband is a hired worker (laborer, construction..). Average income of her family is 174 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD to do business at the market. Other loan members are:

Ms. Nguyen T. T., born in 1972 (member # 010107050013). Loan amount is 240 USD with the intent to purchase ornamental plants to grow and sell;
Ms. H. T. H., born in 1982 (member # 010107050015). Her family works in farming mainly. Loan amount is 240 USD to do business in the market;
Ms. Dang T. V., born in 1950 (member # 010107050012). Average income of her family is 145 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD for raising animals;
Ms. Dao T. A., born in 1976 (member #  010107050016) . She buys and sells eggs at the market daily. Average income of her family is 174 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD to do business in the market.








 
 
