Ms. N. T. Nga, born in 1962 (member # 010107010024). She resides with her husband and 3 children in the hamlet of Luc Canh, Xuan Canh. Her famiL. works mainL. in farming. Everyday she goes to the market to sell and her husband works as a hired worker. Average income of her famiL. is 115 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 265 USD to do business at the market. She is the leader of her loan group which also consists of:

Ms. Tran T. C., born in 1961 (member # 010107010025). Her famiL. works mainL. in farming and raising chickens. Average income of her famiL. is 145 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD to invest in raising chickens;
Ms. Dao T. L., born in 1964 (member # 010107010026). In addition to farming, she also sells vegetables at the market every day. Average income of her famiL. is 115 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 190 USD to raise pigs;
Ms. N. T. Q., born in 1959 (member # 010107010027). Her famiL. also works mainL. in farming and raising animals. In addition she also does hired work. Average income of her famiL. is 174 USD per month. She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD to invest in raising animals;
Ms. Le T. T., born in 1966 (member # 010107010028). She does miscellaneous selling at the market with average income of 12 USD per day. She joined the fund to borrow 240 USD to do business at the market



 


